channel.title: When logout to other place?
channel.description: Well I always wanted to know this. Castlewars has it. When you logout and come backin you go back to the castle wars hall. Is there a way to do that in servers also? I don't want they keep at the same place where they been for the last second before they logout.

item.description:
@jua wrote:

No,
I mean you start for example in varrock.
